Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}My cards, we're about to face the master\N﻿of the kingdom, the strongest Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Let's fight as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrow Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi boy is like a small animal struggling\N﻿for breath as I crush him with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}For I know every single card\N in your entire hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mind Scan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}That gaze that\N pierces through my cards... I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}That feeling's not just my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon's Summon, isn't that right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}He's reading my mind...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}But there's nothing I can do to stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Attacks Impossible!?\N The Invincible Toon Army"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, don't let Pegasus shake you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Be careful, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba is very important to our plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as he's the ﻿one holding the key to the room that holds the contracts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No matter what, you have to get Mokuba back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If we don't get him back,\N what will we tell Master Pegasus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oi, Bakura, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just... going to look for Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do that, Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Geez, that bastard Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's he doing at such\N an important time?! Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi boy, I've already read\N your plan for this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You will first set the Trap Card,\N Hexagram Curse, face-down on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You will then play \NDemon's Summon in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're going to try and tempt my\N﻿Monsters into attacking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(318,447)}﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a card face-down on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Demon's Summon in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay, my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Very well. I will step into your trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}We'll see who is truly\N trapped in the end, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I change Dragon Egger into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Attack the Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Trap activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The one who attacks this card\N falls into its trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dragon Egger's Attack\N goes down by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He trapped Pegasus' Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Demon to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Attack Dragon Egger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Trap Card. activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Trap Displacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Trap Displacement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, I can take a Trap Card used against one of my Monsters and transfer it to the opponent's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Demon's been trapped by the Hexagram Curse instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its Attack Power dropped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know every strategy you have.\N They have no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dragon Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}He's... completely reading\N every one of my strategies...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}How do I fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's too low, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿How's he supposed to fight him like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! If we start giving up, what'll he do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's not the type of guy who'd give up, no matter {\i1}what{\i0} happens to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi... Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's over there! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿﻿That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(326,416)}﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now then, you've got nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Damn it all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You bastard! If you don't obey us,\N you're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura, forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Isn't this interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If I don't obey you, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In that case, my weapon is {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't screw with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Shit...! I can't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura...! These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now, let's take this chance and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Y-Y-Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Shit! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is Team A! Send backup now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}So this is the power of \NPegasus' Millennium Eye...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}There has to be a way to stop his Mind Scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There is no way to stop it, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}He's reading my mind even now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A game is a contest between two minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you can understand the mind of the\N﻿opponent, you are guaranteed to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You don't have the power to step even one foot into the territory of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that includes the world of the game I created as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Allow me to show this to you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is bad! That card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon World is the design of the\N﻿ultimate game world I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Toon characters are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's right! My wonderful Monsters have\N﻿turned into invincible Toon Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Furthermore, all my Toon Monsters ﻿can only be defeated by other Toon Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm sorry, Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon Dragon Egger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Monster\N he has set in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Soldier of Stone\N has been annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿After launching their attacks, my Toon Monsters\N﻿hide themselves deep within Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where your Monsters\N can {\i1}never{\i0} reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The invincible defensive walls of Toon World make me unable to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}This is the card that did in Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I place Toon Mermaid in\N Attack Mode and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Right now, I only have cards suitable for Defense Mode in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}They'll only be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}﻿In that case, I'll test to see if normal Monsters\N can attack Toon Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Elf Swordsman has\N the same Attack as Toon Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}If my attack is successful, they should both be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Elf Swordsman! Attack Toon Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Sword Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Elf Swordsman's sword\N was stopped dead in its tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's no use, Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Monsters have the Special Ability to not be destroyed by normal attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Mermaid Arrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Elf Swordsman was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Damn...! That's too cheap, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}﻿As I thought, attacks against Toon Monsters are impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toons ﻿can only be defeated by Toons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toons are the perfect form of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the power of his Millennium Eye, he sees all my strategies and tactics...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of it, I can't attack head on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there any way I can win this Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will place these two cards face-down on the field, and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Magic Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it a Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(319,447)}﻿My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I play a Monster in Attack Mode,\N﻿It can't defeat the Toons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover, he has that Trap Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This turn, I'll open my set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I activate the Trap Card, Gorgon's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?! The Imp was turned to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This card is a Permanent Trap that turns all of the ﻿opponent's Monsters into a useless statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Furthermore, when your stone Monsters ﻿are destroyed, half their Defense Points\N﻿will be subtracted from your Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In other words, you have no choice but to attack my Toons every single turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What useless attacks they'll be, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now then, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll also Summon another of my lovely, funky friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card, Copycat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a copy card that takes on\N the effect of any card it chooses from the opponent's side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Copy card...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A very loving cat as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And just what card\N do you want to change into?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy, it seems he would like to change into that ﻿Demon's Summon card you played a few turns back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?! My Demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes! And furthermore, Toon World is present on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you aware of what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now it is fully protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And the transformation to your Demon in Toon World is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A new page called "Evil Castle"\N will now open in Toon World
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now come on out here, my Toon Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Demon, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What do you think, Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Doesn't my child give off a\N "definitely lovely" kind of aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus...! You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ohhh~! How scary, how scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon Demon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The stone Imp is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to the effect of Gorgon's Eye, you will lose half the Defense Points of the Imp, 500, from your Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿How was that, Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Doesn't it feel weird being attacked by your own Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It hid in that book again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Damn! Isn't there any way to defeat those Toons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To not only blemish my Monster's dignity but force it to attack me as a Toon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've drawn the Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought. Pegasus not only knows every card in my hand, but every card I draw...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura, what did you do before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Forget that for now.\N Just worry about running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿When this is over, you better explain all this really clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No use! This one's locked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There's an exit up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Y-You saved me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as ﻿Toon World remains on the field, I can't damage him in any of my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't defend myself either...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there any way I can win in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You cannot possibly defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can clearly see your will to fight drifting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well, what do you think? Do you want\N﻿to forfeit the Duel, Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you admit defeat, Mokuba and Kaiba's souls will be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You won't be able to save your grandfather,\N﻿Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please, keep trying, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, my chance of winning is as close to zero as it can possibly get...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yup, there's nowhere left to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Found them! Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Surround em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You won't escape this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Shit! All the guards!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿To give up hope so easily, that's not like you, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You have some sort of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now's not the time to be choosing from a list of strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I give up now, all three of\N﻿their souls will he lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:20:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if my chances of victory \Nare low, I still can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus! I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet on the little possibility\N I have until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is no use, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how hard you struggle,\N you are still finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿With the Millennium Eye reading his hand,\N﻿and Toon World blocking his attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi's attack and defense have both been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tries to bring out his Black Magician/Magical Silk Hats combo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿but he's been completely read by Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Mind Scan didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I get it! Before he can read his mind, he\N﻿just switches minds with the other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Counterattack Begins!\N The Mind Shuffle"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
